🔑 Core Insight (Invariant)

Trust emerges when Warmth and Competence are both expressed above threshold.

* Warmth = perceived safety + alignment
* Competence = perceived capability + reliability

Failure modes:

* Warmth ↑ / Competence ↓ → liked but dismissed
* Competence ↑ / Warmth ↓ → respected but avoided
* Both ↓ → ignored
* Both ↑ → trusted, followed, amplified

